{"tid":1143151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仇思達咁把炮個個屌齊，星期六佢又會有d咩驚人行動？","createTime":"2019-05-07T13:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T00:46:21.000Z","uid":244332,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a58f15bb992bea85b4c590366c745cded5beda8","tid":1143151,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"人人都俾佢屌齊，好想知佢自己星期六又有咩大絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇益友知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />龜縮正龜公"},{"pid":"2a63959c84a9f1d21e56d60651e53f94af95aa3e","tid":1143151,"uid":113373,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:57:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n5月11日 星期六 早上9點 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cbb9f85f1ed5599eec1fc6fdedb48bd997a35de2","tid":1143151,"uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"坐係屋企屌人"},{"pid":"79f49de907f4b57c538bac8dce27d2efd39928b7","tid":1143151,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"會開咪吹奏大灣區"},{"pid":"e7a465ce242566bbeae02816fe8742e463495222","tid":1143151,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbb9f85f1ed5599eec1fc6fdedb48bd997a35de2","tid":1143151,"uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"坐係屋企屌人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T00:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/po